Description: Tactical Gear and Survival Equipment for Professionals.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Former military veterans know firsthand the importance of having reliable and durable gear in the field. Many of the products on the market just didn’t meet the high standards needed in survival and tactical situations. That’s how Anvil Tactical was born. I wanted to create a company that could provide the kind of gear that I knew military personnel and outdoor enthusiasts alike would be able to depend on. From the start, our goal has been to design and manufacture products that are not only practical and functional but also built to last. We started out small, working out of a garage with just a handful of employees. But our commitment to quality quickly gained us a reputation within the industry, and demand for our products grew. Before we knew it, we had outgrown our garage and had to move into a larger facility. Today, Anvil Tactical is a leading provider of tactical gear, survival gear, and camping gear. We have a team of experienced designers and engineers who work tirelessly to ensure that every product we produce meets our high standards. From backpacks to flashlights, we’re proud to offer a wide range of products that are designed to help our customers tackle any challenge they may face in the field. But our commitment to our customers doesn’t end with the products we make. We also believe in providing exceptional customer service and support. We know that our customers depend on our gear to keep them safe and secure, and we take that responsibility seriously. That’s why we offer a satisfaction guarantee on all of our products and why we’re always happy to answer any questions our customers may have. At Anvil Tactical, we’re more than just a company that sells gear. We’re a team of dedicated professionals who are passionate about helping our customers stay safe and prepared. Whether you’re a military veteran, an outdoor enthusiast, or just someone who wants the best gear for their next adventure, we’re here to help.

Description: The Conjuring Arts Research Center is a not-for-profit organization for the preservation and interpretation of magic and its allied arts..
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: The Conjuring Arts Research Center is a not-for-profit organization for the preservation and interpretation of magic and its allied arts. which include psychic phenomenon, hypnosis, deceptive gambling, mentalism, ventriloquism, juggling, and sleight-of-hand techniques. Conjuring Arts functions primarily as a research library,  However, the library itself is only the first in a long list of roles Conjuring Arts plays. By providing its holdings, online database, semi-annually published journal, and performance component to the public, Conjuring Arts strives to preserve the rich histories and traditions of this ancient performing art. It has quickly become a relevant cultural and academic space. Created, in part, to encourage in-depth scholarship devoted to the subject, it has evolved into a resource for performers, historians, writers, collectors, producers of television and film projects, and the general public. With its ever-growing library of books and periodicals, Conjuring Arts developed, and continues to maintain, an expansive collection of magic-related material. Housing both research materials and various rare conjuring antiquities, Conjuring Arts provides a magical opportunity to more fully understand the history and complexities of one of the world’s oldest professions within the context of contemporary life.

Description: Crowdfunding for Independent Media
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: IndieVoices is a crowdfunding site specializing in helping independent media, primarily in the developing world, raise the funds they need. Our goal is to serve as a bridge that connects social investors to high-quality, independent, and socially relevant news and content providers and media companies. Our ideal world is made up of societies, communities, and individuals who are well informed and media literate. It is a world of diverse, independent, and reliable voices that offers all citizens equal access to quality news and information. IndieVoices will power this vision by operating as the vehicle through which you can donate to or invest in new media ventures or in news sources you have known and trusted for decades. Our unique platform, offering several investment options for patient capital, will allow you to directly fund content production, from documentary films to investigative journalism. It will also enable you to fund new digital tools that will enhance news quality or expand access to information for underserved communities. Most important, IndieVoices will democratize and thus reinvent the worlds of media investing and media ownership by introducing to those worlds crowds of individual citizens. Our platform will assist the crowds (formerly known as the audience) to become media proprietors in their own right. In the process, they will support the production and dissemination of quality, independent information worldwide by replacing profit-motivated capital with their own, motivated only by social returns.
